DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
TURNER 2018-0540 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 11, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

Sua sponte, Trent Turner, Attorney Registration No. 0064524, last known business address in Columbus, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to surrender his attorney-registration card and to file an affidavit of compliance on or before November 19, 2018.
